| Layer                                                    | Built-in capability                                                                                            | Recommended DR posture                                                                                                                                                            |
| -------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Autonomous Data Warehouse** (primary data store)       | • Daily incremental backups (60-day retention)<br>• Optional **Autonomous Data Guard** (local or cross-region) | *Minimum*: keep daily backups (meets 12 h RTO / 1 h RPO).<br>*Target*: **Enable cross-region ADG** to achieve < 10 min RTO / ≤ 1 min RPO and protect against region-wide outages. |
| **Oracle Analytics Cloud** (semantic model & dashboards) | Export/import via **OAC snapshot**; object-storage copy                                                        | Schedule **nightly snapshots** to Object Storage, replicate bucket to standby region; restore snapshot post-failover.                                                             |
| **Object Storage** (Data Pump exports, snapshots)        | Cross-region bucket replication                                                                                | Enable **OCI Object-Storage replication** (or Data Sync) for all FAW buckets.                                                                                                     |
| **Identity (IDCS / OCI IAM)**                            | Multi-AD redundancy; optional IDCS bridge                                                                      | For single-tenancy, nothing extra. If separate tenancies, configure **IDCS bridge** or **IDCS export/import** to maintain users & groups.                                         |
| **Orchestration**                                        | OCI **Full Stack DR** (FS-DR) service                                                                          | Build an FS-DR plan that groups ADW, OAC, buckets, DNS records → one-click switchover & monthly drill.                                                                            |
